	<h3>Three Years of YAC</h3>
	<p>The following spie charts show receiving yards per wide receiver, with YAC indicated by the outer slice on each segment. The width of each segment is based on the relative number of receptions, the length of each segment is based on the relative number of receiving yards.</p>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-4">
			<div id="canvas-holder" style="width:100%">
				<canvas tc-chartjs chart-type="Spie" chart-data="players" chart-options="options" ></canvas>
			</div>
			<div style="text-align: center;">

				<select name="teamSelect" id="teamSelect" ng-model="selectedTeam" ng-change="updateDisplay()">
					<div>
						<option ng-repeat="team in teams" ng-value="team.code" >{{team.code}}</option>
					</div>
				</select>

				<select name="yearSelect" id="yearSelect" ng-model="selectedYear" ng-change="updateDisplay()">
					<div >
						<option ng-repeat="year in years" ng-value="year" >{{year}}</option>
					</div>
				</select>

			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-4">
			<div id="canvas-holder" style="width:100%">
